      <title>投资者从债券转向中国股息 ETF 资金激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/china-dividend-etf-flows-surge-as-investors-shift-from-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着 2024 年接近尾声，中国投资者正在加倍投资股息股，流入两只最大的跟踪该主题的交易所交易基金的资金创下了历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/china-dividend-etf-flows-surge-as-investors-shift-from-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 03:54:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>铁矿石价格跌至五周低点，因交易商担心中国需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/iron-ore-hits-five-week-low-as-traders-fret-about-chinese-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国工业利润不佳凸显了该国经济的疲软，尽管钢厂的业绩确实有所改善，但铁矿石价格仍跌至五周多以来的最低水平，跌破每吨 100 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/iron-ore-hits-five-week-low-as-traders-fret-about-chinese-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 02:59:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国工业利润或将出现2000年以来最大年度降幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/china-s-industrial-profits-set-for-steepest-decline-since-2000</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国工业企业利润 11 月份连续第四个月下降，有望创下 2000 年有记录以来的最大年度降幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/china-s-industrial-profits-set-for-steepest-decline-since-2000</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 01:48:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着 Token 创纪录的一年结束，比特币涨势逐渐减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/bitcoin-btc-rally-fizzles-as-token-s-record-breaking-year-winds-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在比特币创纪录的一年即将结束的最后几天，随着投资者评估当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对加密货币行业的支持所带来的剩余动力，比特币的涨势正在减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/bitcoin-btc-rally-fizzles-as-token-s-record-breaking-year-winds-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 01:05:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
